515
00:29:13,708 --> 00:29:14,840
Ow!

516
00:29:14,840 --> 00:29:16,711
Right in the ham hocks.

517
00:29:16,711 --> 00:29:19,496
Tranquilizer dart? Leticia.

518
00:29:19,496 --> 00:29:22,935
