You dream of being a chef.

616
00:35:35,481 --> 00:35:39,093
- Me, a chef?
- It's pretty dumb, right?

617
00:35:39,093 --> 00:35:40,225
- No!

618
00:35:40,225 --> 00:35:42,966
No?

619
00:35:42,966 --> 00:35:44,142
Look, an elephant!

620
00:35:44,142 --> 00:35:47,406
