776
00:43:41,531 --> 00:43:44,012
Ooh.

777
00:43:44,012 --> 00:43:45,057
- Yes!

778
00:43:49,714 --> 00:43:54,196
So you're in San Francisco?
I'm coming, Pickles.

779
